		{
			description: [
				"To whoever finds this, I welcome you to this wonderful world we call home. There will surely be much to discover, fight, learn, and avoid. By reading this book, you accept your reality. I will be in touch. If you ever need to find this menu again, &6&oyou can access it through your inventory in the top left corner or the tabs above the menu. You can also set a keybind in Controls&r."
				"PS: You are never alone. &0Avoid &kthe entity&r&0 at all costs.&r"
			]
			icon: "irons_spellbooks:chained_book"
			id: "15ACD993630984F4"
			rewards: [{
				amount: 150L
				currency: "eternalcurrencies:ancientcoins"
				id: "50664CB77E417D8A"
				ignore_reward_blocking: true
				title: "Some pocket change for the journey ahead"
				type: "eternalcurrencies:currency"
			}]
			subtitle: "Who wrote this?"
