		{
			dependencies: ["15ACD993630984F4"]
			description: [
				"Let's get you fitted with basics, shall we? Any and all good journeys start the same way, by punching a tree."
				"{image:modpack:textures/tree-chopping.png width:156 height:90 align:center}"
				"Something you'll notice upon approaching one of these wooded wonders is the counter at the top of your screen. Yes, in this world, you need only break the bottom block of a tree to knock it down. It will still take a few hits, but it's far more convenient, no? You will also see the amount of logs and any other drops you'll receive from chopping."
			]
			hide_until_deps_complete: true
			id: "5FF18EB0CE40B71B"
			rewards: [
				{
					amount: 100L
					currency: "eternalcurrencies:ancientcoins"
