		{
			dependencies: ["5FF18EB0CE40B71B"]
			description: [
				"So, you've gotten your bearings and some materials. Great job! But it's probably getting dark, isn't it? You'll want to keep your space lit. Not only will it help prevent &6&oeerie nightmares&r, but it will also be crucial when &4&o&lit&r comes for you."
				"By far the easiest way to find light is &6&otorches&r, which you can craft with a stick and any sort of coal."
				"You can make charcoal simply by burning logs. How convenient!"
			]
			hide_until_deps_visible: true
