		{
			dependencies: ["05B83606164A1853"]
			description: [
				"You will no doubt encounter many structures along your adventures, some big, some small. With so much to find, it may feel like you're lost at times, and we don't want that."
				"&o&6Waystones&r are a fantastic relic of old that allow for quick travel across large distances. Using one will allow you to travel to any other waystone you've discovered... for a modest fee, of course. But don't worry. It gets cheaper the farther you go."
				"I &omay&r have one spare that I'd be willing to gift you, but I'd like to be sure you're the type to use it first. That's only fair, no?"
