			dependencies: ["083FB6BC2C2D9609"]
			description: [
				"Do you have an excess of items, even with a nice bag and some chests? Well, have you considered selling your goods?"
				"The &o&6shipping bin&r is a helpful block. By interacting with it, you can deposit all sorts of items and receive ancient coins in return. When midnight hits, you'll be alerted that the contents of the box have been bought and shipped off. Checking the box afterwards, you will see your earnings in its contents."
				"Note that &onot all items are sellable&r, and some items like common ingredients may require more than one before receiving any purchase."
